definitions.definition: A member of a nation of Native Americans indigenous to what is now Wisconsin .

main_definition: A member of a nation of Native Americans indigenous to what is now Wisconsin .

definitions.definition: A village in Jo Daviess County , Illinois , United States .
A city , the county seat of Menominee County , Michigan , United States .
An unincorporated community in Cedar County , Nebraska , United States .
A town in Menominee County , Wisconsin , United States , which is coextensive with and consolidated with the county.
